item.content:encoded:
T-Shirt is designed to adjust to body temperature and environment to keep you cool and dry all day long. Thanks to it's blended 4.5 ounce ring-spun fabric, it has the softest hand in performance tees.
  • 60% Cotton, 40% Polyester
  • Imported
  • Pull On closure
  • Machine Wash

  • T-Shirt dries faster as your body heat rises to help keep cool
  • 40+ UPF rating for UV protection
  • Shoulder-to-shoulder taping

  • Made in USA

  • 19.5in H x 14.5in W x 3in D

  • 60% Cotton, 40% Polyester
  • Imported
  • Pull On closure
  • Machine Wash
  • Pack of two t-shirts in 4.5 oz. ring-spun cotton blend featuring quick-drying technology and tagless neck
  • T-Shirt dries faster as your body heat rises to help keep cool
  • 40+ UPF rating for UV protection
  • Shoulder-to-shoulder taping
